summary: So I almost cried when I watched the trailer. Call me stupid or something else, I don’t care but I need to share my feelings. I...
caption: So I almost cried when I watched the trailer. Call me stupid or something else, I don’t care but I need to share my feelings. I almost cried because she’s like me. For years now I’ve wanted to fly jets faster than the speed of sound. I’ve dreamed of going to space for so long that I don’t remember what it’s like to want my feet on the ground. I’ve wanted to have the power and strength to fight, to stand up for what I know is right and do something. And I’ve never seen a character like me until now. I almost cried because Carol Danvers is everything I want to be in life and more. When I watched that trailer for the first time (and second and third and every other time), I finally found someone like me.
